# ZenLabs Web API - Python SDK

[![fern shield](https://img.shields.io/badge/%F0%9F%8C%BF-Built%20with%20Fern-brightgreen)](https://buildwithfern.com)

Python SDK for the ZenLabs Web API.

## Installation

```sh
pip install "zenlabs-web-python @ git+https://github.com/Zenarate/zenlabs-sdk.git#subdirectory=web/python"
```

## Usage

```python
from zenlabs_sdk import ZenClient

client = ZenClient(
    token="<token>",
    base_url="https://api.zenlabs.com",
)

# List test suites
suites = client.testsuite.suites_list()
```

## Modules

- `testsuite` - Test suite management
- `agentos` - Agent OS / conversations
- `voice` - Voice providers, phone numbers, transcribers, sessions
- `workflow` - Workflow management, nodes, edges, variables

